{"data":[{"name":"87:1","price":"1. Sucikanlah nama Tuhanmu Yang Mahatinggi.","arabic":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5949,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:2","price":"2. Yang menciptakan, lalu menyempurnakan (penciptaan-Nya).","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5950,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:3","price":"3. Yang menentukan kadar (masing-masing) dan memberi petunjuk.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5951,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:4","price":"4. Dan yang menumbuhkan rerumputan.","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5952,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:5","price":"5. Lalu dijadikan-Nya (rumput-rumput) itu kering kehitam-hitaman.","arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحۡوَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5953,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:6","price":"6. Kami akan membacakan (Al-Qur`ān) kepadamu (Muhammad) sehingga engkau tidak akan lupa,","arabic":"سَنُقۡرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5954,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:7","price":"7. kecuali jika Allah menghendaki. Sungguh, Dia mengetahui yang terang dan yang tersembunyi.","arabic":"إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعۡلَمُ ٱلۡجَهۡرَ وَمَا يَخۡفَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5955,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:8","price":"8. Dan Kami akan memudahkan bagimu ke jalan kemudahan (mencapai kebahagiaan dunia dan akhirat).","arabic":"وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5956,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:9","price":"9. Oleh sebab itu, berikanlah peringatan, karena peringatan itu bermanfaat.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5957,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:10","price":"10. Orang yang takut (kepada Allah) akan mendapat pelajaran.","arabic":"سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5958,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:11","price":"11. Dan orang yang celaka (kafir) akan menjauhinya,*(905)","arabic":"وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5959,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*905). Raj`i berarti kembali berputar. Hujan dinamakan raj`i dalam ayat ini, karena hujan itu berasal dari uap yang naik dari bumi ke udara, kemudian turun ke bumi, kemudian kembali ke atas, dan dari atas kembali ke bumi, dan begitulah seterusnya.","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:12","price":"12. (yaitu) orang yang akan memasuki api yang besar (neraka).","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يَصۡلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5960,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:13","price":"13. Selanjutnya dia di sana tidak mati dan tidak (pula) hidup.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحۡيَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5961,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:14","price":"14. Sungguh beruntung orang yang menyucikan diri (dengan beriman).","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5962,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:15","price":"15. Dan mengingat nama Tuhannya, lalu dia salat.","arabic":"وَذَكَرَ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5963,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:16","price":"16. Sedangkan kamu (orang-orang kafir) memilih kehidupan dunia,","arabic":"بَلۡ تُؤۡثِرُونَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5964,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:17","price":"17. padahal kehidupan akhirat itu lebih baik dan lebih kekal.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ وَأَبۡقَىٰٓ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5965,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:18","price":"18. Sesungguhnya ini terdapat dalam kitab-kitab yang dahulu,","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5966,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"87:19","price":"19. (yaitu) kitab-kitab Ibrahim dan Musa.","arabic":"صُحُفِ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ","category":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la"],"ayahNumber":5967,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["87 (Al-A'la)","Al-A'la","Surah Al-A'la","Chapter Al-A'la","A'la","Surah A'la","Chapter A'la","Al A'la","Surah Al A'la","Chapter Al A'la","Surah 87","Chapter 87","The Most High","الأعلى"]}